query:
SELECT DATE_TRUNC('month', first_submission) AS "period",
COUNT(user_id) AS "count!"
FROM (
    SELECT user_id,
      MIN(created_at) AS first_submission
    FROM exercise_slide_submissions
    WHERE course_id = $1
      AND deleted_at IS NULL
    GROUP BY user_id
  ) AS first_submissions
GROUP BY "period"
ORDER BY "period"
